data.description: Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood in Bosqueville ISD, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home offers a serene retreat from the bustling city life. With a cozy fireplace to warm your evenings, you can unwind and relax in comfort. The spacious bedrooms provide ample space for rest and rejuvenation, while the two bathrooms ensure convenience for all. Step outside onto the covered patio and discover an endless pool that invites you to take a refreshing dip on hot summer days, heat it up to relax in the winter or engage in some invigorating laps, this lap pool is perfect for both relaxation and exercise. The quiet neighborhood adds to the allure of this property, providing a peaceful environment for you to enjoy quality time with loved ones or indulge in your favorite hobbies. Escape the chaos of everyday life and embrace the tranquility that awaits at this Bosqueville gem.
